## System Architecture

### High-Level Architecture
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    Client Browser                            │
│              (Next.js 14 + React 18)                        │
└────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────────┘
                     │ HTTP/HTTPS + WebSocket
                     ↓
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│              Next.js Frontend (Port 3000)                    │
│  • Pages Router                                              │
│  • Tailwind CSS + Radix UI                                  │
│  • React Hook Form + Framer Motion                          │
│  • Socket.io Client                                         │
└────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────────┘
                     │ REST API + WebSocket
                     ↓
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│            Express.js Backend (Port 5000)                    │
│  • JWT Authentication + RBAC                                 │
│  • Socket.io Server                                         │
│  • Bull Queue (Redis-based)                                 │
│  • Winston Logging                                          │
│  • Multi-module architecture                                │
└────────┬───────────────┬──────────────┬─────────────────────┘
         │               │              │
         ↓               ↓              ↓
  ┌──────────┐   ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────┐
  │PostgreSQL│   │   Redis     │  │ AI APIs │
  │ (Supabase)│  │ (Cache/Jobs)│  │ Providers│
  │ Port:5432│   │  Port:6379  │  │(External)│
  └──────────┘   └─────────────┘  └─────────┘
```

### Technology Stack

#### Frontend (`/` - root directory)
- **Framework**: Next.js 14.2.30 (Pages Router, not App Router)
- **Language**: TypeScript 5.9.3
- **UI Framework**: React 18.3.1
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS 3.4.13 + Tailwind Animate
- **Component Library**: Radix UI (complete suite) + Lucide React icons
- **Animations**: Framer Motion
- **Forms**: React Hook Form + Joi validation
- **State Management**: React Context API (AuthContext, WebSocketContext)
- **API Client**: Custom hooks (`use-api.ts`, `use-auth.ts`)
- **Charts**: Recharts 3.2.1
- **Markdown**: react-markdown + remark-gfm
- **Real-time**: Socket.io Client
- **Database**: @supabase/supabase-js 2.x, @vercel/postgres
- **Cache**: @vercel/kv (Redis)
- **Supabase Client**: Full-featured client with auth, database, storage, and real-time subscriptions
- **Package Manager**: pnpm 10.18.0

#### Backend (`/server` directory)
- **Runtime**: Node.js 18+ (TypeScript 5.9.3)
- **Framework**: Express 5.1.0
- **Database**: PostgreSQL 15 (via `pg` 8.16.3)
- **Cache/Sessions**: Redis 5.6.0 (ioredis 5.3.2)
- **Queue System**: Bull 4.16.5 (Redis-backed job queues)
- **Authentication**: JWT (jsonwebtoken 9.0.2) + bcryptjs 2.4.3
- **Validation**: Joi 17.13.3 + express-validator 7.2.1
- **Security**: Helmet 8.1.0 + CORS 2.8.5
- **Logging**: Winston 3.11.0
- **Real-time**: Socket.io 4.8.1
- **File Processing**: Multer 1.4.5-lts.1, Sharp 0.33.2
- **Document Generation**: 
  - Handlebars 4.7.8 (templates)
  - Puppeteer 22.0.0 (PDF generation)
  - docx 9.5.1 (Word export)
  - marked 16.4.0, markdown-it 14.1.0 (Markdown processing)
  - turndown 7.2.1 (HTML to Markdown)
- **AI Providers**:
  - OpenAI 4.28.0
  - @google/generative-ai 0.24.1
  - @adobe/pdfservices-node-sdk 4.1.0
  - ai 5.0.70 (Vercel AI SDK)

#### Database Schema (PostgreSQL)
```sql
-- Core Tables
users                 -- User accounts, roles, permissions
projects              -- Project management
documents             -- Document storage (JSONB content in Markdown)
templates             -- Reusable document templates
document_templates    -- Template definitions with variables
ai_providers          -- AI service configurations (OpenAI, Google AI, etc.)
ai_provider_usage     -- Usage tracking and analytics
jobs                  -- Background job queue tracking
audit_logs           -- Action audit trail
security_events      -- Security monitoring
integrations         -- Third-party integrations (Confluence, SharePoint, GitHub)
analytics_events     -- Custom event tracking
baselines            -- Project baselines and snapshots
stakeholders         -- Stakeholder management
process_flows        -- Document generation pipelines
settings             -- System and user settings
```

#### Redis Usage
- **Session Storage**: User sessions with JWT
- **Caching**: Frequent queries, user dashboards, AI provider health
- **Job Queues**: Bull queues for AI generation, document processing, exports
- **Pub/Sub**: Real-time updates, notifications, WebSocket events
- **Rate Limiting**: API throttling and abuse prevention

