### Health Checks

```typescript
// Backend health endpoint
app.get('/health', async (req, res) => {
  try {
    // Check database
    await pool.query('SELECT 1');
    
    // Check Redis
    await redis.ping();
    
    res.json({
      status: 'healthy',
      timestamp: new Date().toISOString(),
      services: {
        database: 'up',
        redis: 'up'
      }
    });
